title: 25 Min CALISTHENICS WORKOUT for Beginners & Intermediates | Follow Along
description:
Build strength with this 25 minute Calisthenics workout suitable for beginners to intermediates. This bodyweight workout can be done with, or without parallettes. Get GRAVITY FITNESS Parallettes https://gravity.fitness/TOMPETOTRAINING

This routine includes the best bodyweight and beginner parallettes exercises you can do at home. Follow along with me if you're looking for a minimalist workout to build an impressive physique.

SUBSCRIBE @TomPetoTraining
